---
import StudioShell from '../../components/studio/StudioShell.astro';
---

<StudioShell>
  <h1>Private Curator Workspace</h1>
  <p class="lead">这里是未来的私人策展台占位页，不属于公开展馆导航。</p>
  <div class="studio-grid">
    <section>
      <h2>Future Studio Routes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>/studio/exhibitions/new</li>
        <li>/studio/exhibitions/[slug]</li>
        <li>/studio/import</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section>
      <h2>Boundary</h2>
      <p>展示界面是展厅，管理界面是策展台。Phase 1 不实现上传、编辑、排序、登录或数据库。</p>
    </section>
  </div>
  <p class="warning">
    Production note: this route should remain blocked by Nginx until authentication or a local-only
    Curator Studio workflow exists.
  </p>
</StudioShell>

<style>
  h1 {
    max-width: 12ch;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Georgia, 'Noto Serif SC', serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 7vw, 5.8rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.95;
  }

  .lead {
    max-width: 38rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
    color: var(--studio-muted);
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 2vw, 1.24rem);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .studio-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  section {
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--studio-line);
  }

  h2 {
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
    color: var(--studio-blue);
    font-family: var(--studio-mono);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--studio-muted);
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  section p,
  .warning {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--studio-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .warning {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--studio-line);
    font-family: var(--studio-mono);
    font-size: 0.76rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .studio-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
